longBusinessSummary: Grande Portage Resources Ltd., an exploration stage company, engages in the exploration and development of natural resource properties in the United States and Canada. It holds 100% interest in the Herbert gold property consisting of 91 unpatented mining claims located in north of Juneau, Alaska. The company was incorporated in 1984 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
